title: IFaxServer::put_DiscountRateStartMinute (faxcom.h)
description: Sets or retrieves the DiscountRateStartMinute property for a FaxServer object. The DiscountRateStartMinute property is a number that represents the minute the discount period begins. The discount period applies only to outgoing fax transmissions. (Put)
